      "summary": "特性规格文档的根章节，概述 Tabs/TabContent 事件回调的完整行为规格。"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "document-section:sha256:ec8d0ed7cfec8fb3555eba8d276b60d4b5af322d3cc483746c7d668d52647afd",
      "summary": "概述部分，列出特性名称、编号、优先级、目标版本等元数据。"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "document-section:sha256:f99389d4e5d8abfc77015c152bed6df77126801312a7ea5f93d84da0e497132c",
      "summary": "本次变更范围说明，指出无新增变更，为已有实现补录，覆盖全量事件回调。"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "document-section:sha256:d39981fb12e0298977cbebafb20fdee02762adbad9326dec9d4e26c6e410881e",
      "summary": "输入文档列表，包括设计文档和 SDK 知识库。"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "document-section:sha256:ec1a3c6e8b6ce2853288094875d378e11dacf50ab1b4356f3f985f8dfff609af",
      "summary": "用户故事章节，包含六个用户故事，分别描述监听标签页切换、选中/取消选中、标签栏点击、切换动画、手势滑动、内容切换拦截和滑动事件的需求。"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "document-section:sha256:422a50c32fb308af33e089183e3b6403a63be0843d85a7f305e03adfa8b4f828",
      "summary": "US-1: 监听标签页切换事件，通过 onChange 回调获取新索引。"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "document-section:sha256:f9e4c20c6311ac94becef8e28f13c9046719e95e888d56696fa1205a534af628",
      "summary": "US-2: 监听标签选中/取消选中事件，通过 onSelected 和 onUnselected 回调获取索引。"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "document-section:sha256:1b1a6d342f17f082e1863b838da50580e9c06e9593f310ca1febe9ecb94f76d6",
      "summary": "US-3: 监听标签栏点击事件，通过 onTabBarClick 回调获取被点击项索引。"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "document-section:sha256:2e5f9a10415229c4e5ae7eeff8293bffae41e5be355b1d8c6071c83f510e60fc",
      "summary": "US-4: 监听切换动画事件，通过 onAnimationStart/onAnimationEnd 回调获取动画事件数据。"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "document-section:sha256:e74e0e070517513b0117db97f64803e9928b6fe12f688aa911a8046b82c45650",
      "summary": "US-5: 监听手势滑动事件，通过 onGestureSwipe 回调获取滑动偏移和速度。"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "document-section:sha256:b6ea7bfa01fdeffbc5e1464c75d7410250900aa4b2d582bff9b49b3d5aea4b4a",
      "summary": "US-6: 监听内容切换拦截和滑动事件，通过 onContentWillChange 拦截切换，通过 onContentDidScroll 获取滑动偏移。"
    },
    {
